    "## Data Preparation\n",
    "\n",
    "The following preprocessing steps are performed:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Data Cleaning**\n",
    "   - Handling missing or inconsistent player identifiers\n",
    "   - Removing irrelevant or incomplete records\n",
    "\n",
    "2. **Aggregation**\n",
    "   - SkillCorner match-level data aggregated to season-level per player\n",
    "\n",
    "3. **Merging**\n",
    "   - Wyscout and SkillCorner datasets joined using a player ID mapping table\n",
    "\n",
    "4. **Filtering**\n",
    "   - Minimum minutes thresholds applied to ensure sample reliability\n",
    "   - Focus restricted to attacking roles (e.g., forwards and attacking midfielders)\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Rationale\n",
    "\n",
    "Filtering by minutes ensures that all evaluated players have a sufficient sample size, reducing noise and improving the reliability of comparisons."
