    "## Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "To better capture player profiles, several derived features are constructed:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Physical Metrics**\n",
    "  - Top speed\n",
    "  - High-intensity running distance\n",
    "  - Acceleration-based indicators\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Production Metrics**\n",
    "  - Goals, xG, shots\n",
    "  - Efficiency measures (e.g., xG per shot)\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Movement & Activity**\n",
    "  - Off-ball movement\n",
    "  - Involvement in dangerous areas\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Design Philosophy\n",
    "\n",
    "Features are selected and engineered with an emphasis on:\n",
